pkgmetadata.longdescription: Soybean Nested Association Mapping Dataset // Genomic and multi- environmental soybean data. Soybean Nested Association Mapping (SoyNAM) project dataset funded by the United Soybean Board (USB). See doi.org/10.1534/g3.118.200332 and doi.org/10.1534/g3.117.300300. BLUP function formats data for genome-wide prediction and association analysis.
